# ========================== PREFIX ==========================
# change   Modifications to existing features
# chore    Changes that do not affect the user experience
# docs     Documentation changes
# feat     Addition of a new feature
# fix      Bug fixes and similar corrections
# perf     Changes related to performance improvements
# refactor Code changes that do not affect behavior
# release  Used when creating a release
# revert   Reverting a previous change
# test     Changes related to testing

# ========================== FORMAT ==========================
# <PREFIX>[optional scope]: <description>
#
# [optional body]
#
# [optional footer]
#
# A breaking change must be explicitly indicated by including
# `BREAKING CHANGE` either as a prefix or in the footer.
